{"tid":611083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳大橋穿梭巴士設港澳及港珠兩線　最密3分鐘一班車","createTime":"2018-03-30T15:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T02:35:58.000Z","uid":64694,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7f2d374038764d4db5b0688bccde05214ccbfa93","tid":611083,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋最快今年中通車，澳門引述大橋管理局消息指，來往3地口岸的穿梭巴士，主要設「港澳」及「<span style=\"color: red;\">港珠</span>」兩條路線，正常班次每10分鐘一班，亦會按情況加密至3至5分鐘一班，兩線共投放140部穿梭巴士。<br />\n<br />\n另外港珠澳大橋管理局稱，如非超車，大橋需靠右行駛，跟隨內地規則。當車輛到達港澳兩地口岸後，才需改回靠左行駛。至於大橋的收費站，全部可使用電子繳費，人工收費則只收人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n局方早前已宣布，容許於港珠澳大橋行駛的車輛，主要是持有粵港兩地車牌車輛、擁有澳門配額的港籍單牌車輛、港澳兩地車牌車輛、辦理一次性配額的車輛，以及3地政府商議可駛經大橋的其他車輛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2011950/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E7%A9%BF%E6%A2%AD%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%A8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%8A%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E5%85%A9%E7%B7%9A%E3%80%80%E6%9C%80%E5%AF%863%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E4%B8%80%E7%8F%AD%E8%BB%8A?mtc=10027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2011950%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E6%25A2%25AD%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25B7%259A%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25AF%25863%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25BB%258A%3Fmtc%3D10027&d=N3kyYz3JVlASKvAtJwNgn54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=c738c7a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2011950/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E7%A9%BF%E6%A2%AD%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%A8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%8A%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E5%85%A9%E7%B7%9A%E3%80%80%E6%9C%80%E5%AF%863%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E4%B8%80%E7%8F%AD%E8%BB%8A?mtc=10027</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「港豬」線</span></span><img src=\"/